data.description: What a beauty!   Come and see this immaculate home that has been extremely well maintained!  This amazing home has custom plantation blinds throughout, new carpet in 2 bedrooms (there is enough left to put in the primary bedroom if desired), fresh paint throughout (with the exception of the primary bath), gorgeous fireplace, tons of storage and large rooms!  The washer/dryer and the refrigerator remain with the property in AS-IS condition.  Come and see this one today!
